<p>At the end of the day, I'm just a kid from Toronto who had a dream and worked hard to make it a reality. I'm proud of where I've come from and what I've accomplished, but I'm always looking ahead to the future. Who knows what's next for me? Maybe I'll drop another album, or maybe I'll take on a new venture entirely. All I know is that whatever I do, I'll do it with passion and dedication. That's just who I am.</p>
